          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "I have family responsibilities. Can I really make this work?",
            "answer": "<p>Absolutely. Our whole-life approach is designed for professionals balancing multiple commitments. We help you create a transition timeline that respects your family needs. Many of our members successfully pivoted while managing parenting, caregiving, and other responsibilities.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
